<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪把唐僧绑在了一个漆黑的房间里，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16960</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后他又把八戒和悟净拖了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们还是无法脱掉那背心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31332</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪把他们扔在了一个角落里，然后又走向唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31333</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37770</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一直在等你。”妖怪说着露出了邪恶的笑容。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“放我们走吧。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要去西天取经。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道。”妖怪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还知道吃了你会长生不老。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58107</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是谁？”悟净在角落里问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58108</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪转过身来。“我是独角兕大王。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69551</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的朋友很快就会找到我们的。”八戒说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他很厉害的。他要是知道你抓了我们，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他会毁了你整座山的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>独角兕大王笑了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁是你们的朋友？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他叫孙悟空。”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪的笑容消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是那个大闹天宫的孙悟空吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92176</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪的声音听上去有点儿紧张。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对，就是他。”悟净说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所有天兵天将都打不过他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“连玉帝都怕他呢。”八戒补充说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>独角兕大王挺起了胸膛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我才不怕他呢！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪走出了房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他刚出来，却又担心了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126643</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那猴子很厉害。”他自言自语道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126644</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128999</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我得用我的特殊兵器。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挽起了袖子，露出了手臂上的金刚圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空拿着食物回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为没有看到唐僧他们，他就抬头看了看那庙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>庙消失了。原来的地方只有一个黑黑的洞穴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空摇摇头。“那庙是虚构的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159056</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一定是妖怪变出来骗人的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159057</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空气得用力跺了一下脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们为什么不相信我呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我警告过他们这里有妖怪的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他放下食物朝着洞穴跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“开门！”悟空大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要是不开，我就打烂你的山！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>洞门开了，独角兕大王走了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你叫什么叫？”妖怪说，“太过分了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“放了唐僧他们！”悟空吼道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不！”独角兕大王交叉着双臂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是不会放了他们的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207464</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们是小偷，偷了我珍贵的背心。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在撒谎。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“唐僧是个诚实的好人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不会偷东西。我是不会相信你......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是那头猪偷的。”妖怪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦。”悟空挠了挠头说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧。那我相信你，但这一点儿都不重要！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230004</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空抽出了金箍棒，朝着妖怪打去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪躲开了，金箍棒砸在了山的一侧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>岩石炸开，滚下了山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246981</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪瞪着悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我记得你。玉帝怕你，但我不怕！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他朝着悟空冲过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空又挥起了金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪用手臂挡住了。哐当！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”妖怪大叫一声，不停地揉着手臂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跪在地上，背对着悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的金箍棒可不是普通的兵器。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它非常重。”他注意到妖怪挽起了袖子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>281386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你想干什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>独角兕大王迅速转过身来，举起了金钢圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空立刻感觉自己被一股力量吸向那个金钢圈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300691</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空用尽所有力气跳到空中，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300692</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304042</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但金箍棒还是被吸走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>金箍棒被吸到了那金钢圈中消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>